metadata.name: You Devised Me to Question Everything
metadata.description:
*Owner of NFT has the option of receiving a signed print of the purchased NFT*
"You Devised Me to Question Everything" is about being in what you think is a healthy relationship until that relationships ends. Without love-blinders on, plus time to reflect, I personally realized all of the reasons why my ex partner and I were wrong for each other-- even though during our relationship we thought we were perfect together. I have created a poem for this artwork and it goes like this:

You toyed with my heart
You played with my head
As if I were merely a pawn
in your wicked game of chess
And after you left
the fog lifted so I could see so clearly 
that I had an epiphany,

You devised me to question everything.
